---
---

<section class="relative pt-36 pb-24 sm:pt-44 sm:pb-32 px-6 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Ambient copper glow -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[600px] -z-10 pointer-events-none"
    style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(184, 133, 74, 0.12) 0%, transparent 60%);">
  </div>

  <!-- Subtle grid lines -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 opacity-[0.025] pointer-events-none"
    style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgb(237 237 234) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgb(237 237 234) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 80px 80px;">
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    <!-- Top metadata bar -->
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-rule pb-3 mb-12 sm:mb-16">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <span class="inline-block w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-copper animate-pulse"></span>
        <p class="mono-label">Straw Dogs LLC / 001</p>
      </div>
      <p class="mono-label hidden sm:block">A Boutique Ghostwriting + Authority Architecture Firm</p>
    </div>

    <p class="eyebrow mb-8">For Hybrid Publishers / A Working Note</p>

    <!-- Logo + Display headline composition -->
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-10 lg:gap-12 items-start">
      <!-- Logo block -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-3 fade-in">
        <div class="relative max-w-[220px] lg:max-w-none rounded-sm overflow-hidden"
          style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fafaf7 0%, #efece4 100%); padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem 1.25rem; box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.5px rgba(184, 133, 74, 0.25), 0 0 40px -10px rgba(184, 133, 74, 0.25), 0 30px 60px -30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);">
          <img
            src="/images/logo.jpg"
            alt="Straw Dogs Development"
            class="w-full h-auto object-contain"
            style="mix-blend-mode: multiply;"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Headline block -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-9">
        <h1 class="display text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl leading-[1.0] text-balance mb-8" style="font-weight: 500;">
          Story is a technology.<br />
          <span class="display-italic" style="font-weight: 500;">Not a talent.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="font-display italic text-xl sm:text-2xl leading-[1.4] text-bone-soft max-w-3xl text-balance"
          style="font-variation-settings: 'opsz' 144;">
          A handful of titles a year define a publisher; the rest fade. The difference is rarely
          the cover, the marketing budget, or the launch. It's the architecture of the manuscript itself.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
